title: Steve Wilkos Lie Detector Shocker
description:
LIE DETECTOR SHOCKER:

***********************************************************************************



Valentina's four year-old daughter said Valentina's sister's boyfriend, Nefye molested her! Nefye denies it. Valentina's husband, Christian, has known Nefye for a long time and is shocked that Nefye might have done it. Nefye's girlfriend, Samantha, believes the accusations and has packed up her car and left Nefye behind. When Steve reads the lie detector test, even he is shocked with the result!




***********************************************************************************
